OL,3,CJedburgh Pool has been saved from
OL,4,Cclosure
OL,6,FJedburgh Pool has been saved from
OL,7,Fclosure after being granted #40,000 to
OL,8,Fcontinue serving the local community.
OL,10,FJedburgh Leisure Facilities Trust
OL,11,F(JLFT), who runs the swimming pool,
OL,12,Fsays the Jedburgh Pool was at risk of
OL,13,Fclosure due to the 'huge' increase in
OL,14,Fenergy costs and the 'outstanding'
OL,15,Fdebt.
