OL,3,CJedburgh Pool has been saved from
OL,4,Cclosure
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council has funded
OL,7,Fthe #40,000 from financial reserves.
OL,8,FHowever, the Council has asked for
OL,9,Ffuture oversight on the financial
OL,10,Fplans operated by the Jedburgh Leisure
OL,11,FFacilities Trust to ensure its long
OL,12,Fterm future.
OL,14,FBefore the Council meeting on 29
OL,15,FAugust 2024, a crowdfunding page was
OL,16,Fset up to raise #20,000 in the hope to
OL,17,Fkeep the facility open - locals banded
OL,18,Ftogether to raise more than #6,000.
