OL,3,CJedburgh Pool has been saved from
OL,4,Cclosure
OL,6,FThe Trust said the pool would have to
OL,7,Fclose immediately without emergency
OL,8,Fcash from the Council, on 27 August
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FBilly Robson, manager at Jedburgh
OL,12,FPool, says despite the financial
OL,13,Fstruggles there is high interest in
OL,14,Fusing the community pool.
